data.description: Come see this spectacular Diyanni built home located in a great location, sought-after neighborhood of Brittany Woods. You will love the openness of this home along with its updates on flooring and features, including 9' ceilings on the first floor, 4 bedrooms, 2 1/2 baths, soaking tub, loft area for relaxing, an extra-large work room off the garage, and a bonus room above. Family room has a gas-log fireplace and is pre-wired for surround sound. Basement has poured walls and appears to be 8ft tall with a full bath rough-in. The open crawl area has a poured concrete floor. Additional storage shed for tools or lawnmower. Located on a no outlet street with No HOA on a large lot. Don't miss your chance to own this beautiful home. A New Roof will be installed on home in January.
